  <static seed="53" source="Contrib/PCC/BasicAlgebra/Factoring/factoring100.pg">
    <statement><p>Factor the given polynomial.</p>
<p><m>{54x^{5}y^{3}+24x^{4}y^{3}+48x^{3}y^{3}}=</m> <fillin characters="31" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>6x^{3}y^{3}\mathopen{}\left(9x^{2}+4x+8\right)</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>The greatest common factor is <m>6x^3y^{3}</m>, so we can factor the polynomial as follows:</p>
<p><m>{54x^{5}y^{3}+24x^{4}y^{3}+48x^{3}y^{3}}={6x^{3}y^{3}\mathopen{}\left(9x^{2}+4x+8\right)}</m></p>
</solution>
